g++ *filename*     .\a.exe      Manually run program from teminal

ctrl + /    --> makes all selected lines comments 
                            or
                makes the line youre on a comment withought selection
                
main + enter  --> cpp code snippet for main function
ctrl + click  --> gives info about the header file etc
alt + shift   --> (alt + shift) then use mouse to drag down to make multiple cursors
alt + arrow keys    --> L and R arrow switches tabs in VS Code U and D arrow moves the line up or down